dwaymenu - dynamic wayland menu
====================
dwaymenu is an efficient dynamic menu for Wayland.


Requirements
------------
In order to build dwaymenu you need the Wayland header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dwaymenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dwaymenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dwaymenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
